body.description: This extra-large 5 quart digital air fryer features Oster DiamondForce nonstick coating, Oster's longest-lasting nonstick yet. DiamondForce Nonstick is infused with diamond particles that form a structural matrix, creating a stronger coating to provide easy food release and superior nonstick performance over time. This Oster air fryer has a digital display and 8 preset functions including Fries, Chicken, Fish, and Dehydrate, so you can easily make all your favorite meals, with 99.5% less oil than deep frying (compared to 4L-capacity deep fryers). It offers an extra-large capacity, detachable frying basket, overheat protection, and nonslip feet. And the PFOA-free, diamond-infused nonstick surface means hassle-free cleanup.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Make great family meals with Oster’s longest-lasting nonstick. Food belongs on your plate, not stuck to the pan!

What is DiamondForce? It’s Oster’s longest-lasting nonstick. It makes family meals easy to cook and cleanup a breeze.

Fried Favorites, High-Performance Nonstick XL Air Fryer 5-quart, extra-large-capacity air fryer is perfect for healthier frying, and making family meals from hearty breakfasts to crunchy snacks. Our longest-lasting nonstick is infused with diamond particles to add natural hardness and durability, so food ends up on your plate and not stuck to the pan. DiamondForce is scratch resistant, easy to clean, and will be a hero in your kitchen, meal after meal.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 22, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great size and intuitive controls; stays cool on the outside; quiet
reviews.reviewText: This is my second air fryer. CR ranked it Very Good and my other one Excellent. I like this one better. It has a larger basket which not only holds more food but also gives you more room to reach in and turn the food over during cooking. The inner basket lifts out easily from the cooking basket, with the push of a button. It is quiet in operation and stays cool on the outside. You can put one hand on the top to steady it while you pull the cooking basked out of the machine using its handle. And it won't heat up whatever you have near it on your counter. It has a bunch of automatic features--you can set it for fish, or chicken or French fries, etc. But if you want to set the time and temperature manually, they have made it easy and intuitive. It comes with only limited instructions, but you don't need them once you figure out that to lift the inside basket out of the outside basket you slide the tab away from you with your thumb, which exposes a button hidden underneath. Push the button and lift it upwards and out with the handle. Easy. And foolproof. You can't accidentally drop the outer basket. If you want detailed information on settings for cooking various foods, beyond the brief list provided, buy a book on cooking with air fryers. Amazon has them. Oh, and as to smell, when I preheated it I got just a whiff of smell as it burned off some oil or coating, but that odor went away as fast as it arrived. No smell during operations.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 13, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars powerhouse and easy to clean

reviews.reviewText: Me encantó, le cabe bastante y funciona a la perfección, tengo 5 meses usándola y no me ja decepcionado. Recomiendo tener despejada ña parte de atrás donde es la salida del aire caliente.

En realidad solo es una resistencia y un ventilador en una caja que parece cacerola, muy simple pero hace bien la función, igual que en cualquier maquina los programas automáticos son una sugerencia de tiempo/temperatura, al final siempre acabo poniendo mas tiempo a mas temperatura.Cumple bien, me agrada, se limpia muy fácil, solo le queda un saborcito curioso a la comida, seguro por el tema de la resistencia, veré si se le pasa con el tiempo o si es de esas cosas que "te acostumbras"
Excelente calidad, muy linda, fácil de limpiar,

Es justo lo que uno espera (porque lo ha leído) de una freidora de aire: Es bonita, funcional, fácil de limpiar y deja la comida en el punto exacto para comerla. Por supuesto, hay que aprender los tiempos y en ocasiones abrir la canasta una y otra vez para corroborar que la comida está en el punto exacto pero el resultado es espectacular. Lo que mejor nos ha quedado (hasta ahora) son los molletes y los cortes de carne gruesos. La carne queda jugosa, dorada por fuera y de término medio a tres cuartos por dentro. Totalmente satisfecho

La verdad que algunos comentarios me hacían dudar de adquirirla, pero afortunadamente la mía llegó impecable ya voy para los dos meses con ella y funciona sin problemas. La encontré a un super precio, tanto que se agotaba al poco tiempo de estar disponible. Si estas buscando una freidora de aire, este modelo es ideal, su capacidad, materiales y su fácil manejo es genial. Un plus sería que tenga recetario como otras marcas, pero con una simple búsqueda en internet encuentras toda clase de platillos que puedes hacer en la freidora, sin duda la recomiendo mucho.
